page.title: 10SALTERBECK INDUSTRIAL ESTATE
page.content: {Salterbeck}has an{industrial estate which deals in many aspects of business.Such as making fuses,producing plastic crisp packets etc.Also Salterbeck estate has a number of{warehouses}which stock almost anything from clothes to toilet roll.Salterbeck estate is made up of {Salterbeck 1,2 and 3. Salterbeck 1 makes fuses for special heavy duty equipment.{Salterbeck 2}deals with making plastic packets for crisps and confectionaries.{Salterbeck 3}designs and makes computer panels which are used in controlling factories and nuclear works.
